{"tid":2346012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒促拜登「武裝台灣」威懾北京","createTime":"2020-12-30T03:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T08:24:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"616fadb59d3740da0bbc08353f3ead77b20ae232","tid":2346012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201230/Y46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201230%2FY46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=7fec7e70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201230%2FY46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI%2F&h=5aebc3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201230/Y46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美媒促拜登「武裝台灣」威懾北京<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vyJFumdfHogWObkv-ajawHjoO_0=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D5GCTLG64RCOZEAUNGFAR5Z2YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvyJFumdfHogWObkv-ajawHjoO_0%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD5GCTLG64RCOZEAUNGFAR5Z2YA.jpg&h=631d2002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美關係角力之際，美國總統當選人拜登的外交政策受世界矚目，美國《華爾街日報》發表評論指，拜登想穩住美國在亞洲的盟友，台灣是他首個考驗，評論認為拜登應以威懾大陸為目標，協助武裝台灣，延續特朗普政府力助台灣更新軍備的路線，才能令亞洲盟友安心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解放軍試射東風-5恫嚇<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》編輯室前日發表社評指，日本防衞副大臣中山泰秀日前受訪時稱，希望拜登明確表態對台政策，讓日本妥善因應台灣議題。同時，台灣民意越來越反對統一，不能排除中共在拜登任內，跨越110英里的台海發動軍事行動的可能。文章建議美國以嚇阻為目標，優先要務是「武裝台灣」，讓台灣可在即使沒有美國支援下，也能讓大陸進犯付出慘痛代價：「如果拜登想讓美國的亞洲盟友安心，台灣是他的首個重大考驗」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大陸解放軍動作不斷，中部戰區前日發佈關於戰略火箭軍的影片，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於美國MQ-4C海神無人偵察機，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》"},{"pid":"8c22b91287dbbdf5efff5decbd961c7fbb76ed16","tid":2346012,"uid":198175,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"係就賣神盾驅逐艦同F35B畀台軍"},{"pid":"8bbbc77bdc0a69ac8372b7d9a34a97e679d8f79c","tid":2346012,"uid":8308,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"促拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如促中共"},{"pid":"f6887f646f9e3163e042debec6e7ba1de83587a0","tid":2346012,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcQUZYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcQUZYq.png&h=2e116a19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"078a7d7261848e772864baf453cc2e882ae0c88c","tid":2346012,"uid":112748,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"616fadb59d3740da0bbc08353f3ead77b20ae232","tid":2346012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201230/Y46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201230%2FY46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=7fec7e70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201230%2FY46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI%2F&h=5aebc3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201230/Y46ZPK7JD5BAFEQOCF5MVGIGDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美媒促拜登「武裝台灣」威懾北京<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vyJFumdfHogWObkv-ajawHjoO_0=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D5GCTLG64RCOZEAUNGFAR5Z2YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvyJFumdfHogWObkv-ajawHjoO_0%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD5GCTLG64R